{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"631c5f4f64","title":"部队争取在吴起镇金汤镇集结休息","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7604d84f42","index":0,"year":1935,"month":10,"day":16,"articleId":"631c5f4f64"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"262809e9ac","type":"paragraph","text":"部队争取在吴起镇金汤镇集结休息”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"631c5f4f64"},{"id":"7624938fcf","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年10月16日）彭","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"631c5f4f64"},{"id":"3af98ce0c6","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）敌情无新得。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"631c5f4f64"},{"id":"d9e80f0a3c","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）一纵队本日行五十里到达木瓜城一带宿营，明（十七）日拟进至铁边城、吊掌、田百户之线约五六十里，后日则向吴起镇”进。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"631c5f4f64"},{"id":"2537527ad5","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）二、三纵队明日应向金汤镇进。在敌情许可下，每日行五十至六十里，准备以三天至四天行程到达金汤镇。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"631c5f4f64"},{"id":"672b654570","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）如追敌停顿，我军应在吴起镇、金汤镇集结休息一二天，查明保安“、靖边情形，然后分路袭取之，即在吴起镇、保安、靖边地域休息整理扩大，并征集资材，解决冬衣问题，一面派人去苏区取联络。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"631c5f4f64"},{"id":"2b2bc3c731","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）现在每天走路不多，请令各部利用时间进行教育并尽力改善给养。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"631c5f4f64"},{"id":"1f7c4198d7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"631c5f4f64"},{"id":"1c7f0c2bab","type":"paragraph","text":"十六日十九时TI]这是毛泽东给红军陕甘支队司令员彭德怀的电报。12]吴起镇，今名吴旗镇，为陕西省吴旗县县治。[3]金汤镇，位于今陕西省志丹县西部。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"631c5f4f64"},{"id":"cf64a8ccfd","type":"paragraph","text":"1935年10月19日，毛泽东率领部队到达陕北苏区吴起镇，长征胜利结束。图为吴起镇全景","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"631c5f4f64"},{"id":"60121b5e3d","type":"paragraph","text":"长船是省窗者化征县省博融","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"631c5f4f64"},{"id":"6d7de9d074","type":"paragraph","text":"电行是梅福康吴起镇的火炬碑文。《毛主席在陕北》（素描《吴起镇会师》（油画）","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"631c5f4f64"}],"page":{"id":"a9836d45a1","publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"631c5f4f64","start":242,"end":245}}}},"__N_SSG":true}